<font size=3 face=Arial>
<b>An update from your "hosts" at P.O.V.<br>(April 3, 1997)</b><p>
</font>
<font size=2 face="Arial">
We've had a notice on this page for several weeks saying that we're having
trouble raising money to maintain this site and might have to make it
"read-only."<p>

We've received quite a few comments from people who don't want to see that
happen. Please understand that we don't want to see it happen either, and
we're doing everything we can to prevent it.  <p>

Because of several new developments, the site will remain active at least
until the end of April.  If you can help financially, please contact us at
<a href="stories@pov.org">stories@pov.org</a>.<p>

(We''ll be posting a longer message on this subject in topic 51 on friday.)
</font>
</center>
